          <span style="font-face:arial;font-size:10pt;color:darkgreen;font-weight:light;">Best Future Forests</span> is located at the <a href="https://ualberta.ca">University of Alberta</a>.<br /><br/>
          <a href="https://ualberta.ca"><img src="/static/img/UofA_logo.png" height="60"></a>
        </div>

        <!-- Breedbase, BTI, BRAPI -->
